<lb n="0468b16" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="001" type="卷"/><note n="0468016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】麗本</note><cb:jhead>佛說甘露經陀羅尼
<note n="0468017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呪〕－【三】，＋（唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯）【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0468017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呪【大】，〔－〕【宋】【元】【明】，呪唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯【元】【明】</note>
<app n="0468017"><lem wit="【大】">呪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg>
<rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">唐于闐三藏實叉難陀譯</rdg></app></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0468b17" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0468b18" ed="T"/><cb:div type="dharani"><p xml:id="pT21p0468b1801" cb:type="dharani">南無素嚕皤耶<note place="inline">一</note>怛他揭多<note place="inline">去聲<note n="0468018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔呼之〕－【明】</note><note n="0468018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">呼之【大】，〔－〕【明】</note><app n="0468018"><lem wit="【大】">呼之</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app></note>耶<note place="inline">二</note>怛姪他
<lb n="0468b19" ed="T"/><note place="inline">三</note>唵<note place="inline">四</note>素嚕素嚕<note place="inline">五</note>皤囉素嚕<note place="inline">六</note>皤羅素嚕<note place="inline">七</note>莎
<lb n="0468b20" ed="T"/>呵<note place="inline">八</note></p>
<lb n="0468b21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT21p0468b2101">右取水一掬呪之七遍散於空中。其水一渧
<lb n="0468b22" ed="T"/>變成<note n="0468019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">十＝中【宋】</note><note n="0468019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">十【大】，中【宋】</note><app n="0468019"><lem wit="【大】">十</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】">中</rdg></app>斛甘露。一切餓鬼並得飲之。無有乏
<lb n="0468b23" ed="T"/>少皆悉飽<note n="0468020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">滿＋（佛說甘露經陀羅尼）【元】【明】</note><note n="0468020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">滿【大】，滿佛說甘露經陀羅尼【元】【明】</note><app n="0468020"><lem wit="【大】">滿</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【元】【明】">滿佛說甘露經陀羅尼</rdg></app>。</p></cb:div>
